441
00:39:46,990 --> 00:39:52,770
Since we are now husband and wife, I need to say some things beforehand.

442
00:39:54,050 --> 00:39:56,480
Say it.

443
00:39:56,480 --> 00:40:00,490
We've made a vow to the Great Lake of Eastern Wilderness,

444
00:40:00,490 --> 00:40:02,870
