445
00:40:02,870 --> 00:40:06,410
You then can't be unfaithful to me for all eternity.

446
00:40:06,410 --> 00:40:10,420
I'm a person who separates love and hate very clearly.

447
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:12,920
I can't allow any flaws.

448
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,960
If you break my heart...

449
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:17,120
What will you do?

450
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:22,570
If you break my heart, those vows will be voided.

451
00:40:22,570 --> 00:40:25,550
I will abandon you and never see you again.

452
00:40:27,500 --> 00:40:30,840
If I break your heart, you'll abandon me.

453
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:33,710
Aren't you then granting me my wish?

454
00:40:33,710 --> 00:40:36,230
I'm not kidding with you!

